title: Tuesday Pt2: Biggest surprises of the 2022 season; Dan Hanzus' Power Rankings
itunes:title: Tuesday Pt2: Biggest surprises of the 2022 season; Dan Hanzus' Power Rankings
description:
Part Two of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty looking around the league and sharing what’s surprised them most about the beginning of the 2022 season. Later, they’re joined by England personality Johnny Vaughan and he delivers a segment full of comedy and then they’re joined by Dan Hanzus for his latest version of his power rankings.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
